00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:29,000
 God also just powerfully allows us to rest in our identity that he gives us.

516
00:30:29,000 --> 00:30:39,000
 Not that other people try to give us or that we think we can somehow earn, but that's never stable.

517
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:43,000
 And so he renews you through that.

518
00:30:43,000 --> 00:30:47,000
 And I believe he is speaking that over some of you even right now,

519
00:30:47,000 --> 00:30:51,000
 just reminding you of your identity, that you are loved.

520
00:30:51,000 --> 00:30:55,000
 You're not your performance or your lack of your performance.

521
00:30:55,000 --> 00:30:59,000
 You are a beloved child of God.

522
00:30:59,000 --> 00:31:08,000
 And he wants you to be able to find rest and peace in your identity in him.

523
00:31:08,000 --> 00:31:13,000
 And then, of course, a final blessing of this renewal is just simply we get to enjoy,

524
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:16,000
 and that's a grace blessing, just be in relationship with God.

525
00:31:16,000 --> 00:31:20,000
 We get to enjoy our relationship with God.

526
00:31:20,000 --> 00:31:27,000
 Now, so how can we respond to this message?

527
00:31:27,000 --> 00:31:32,000
 How can we start living in a sanctuary of his power and his love?

528
00:31:32,000 --> 00:31:41,000
 Well, for one, you actually need to set aside time to rest and to spend unhurried time with God.

529
00:31:41,000 --> 00:31:46,000
 So if you're not do that and you just keep doing what you're doing,

