00:32:33,000 --> 00:32:36,000
 Maybe it's during the week, maybe it's in the weekend.

541
00:32:36,000 --> 00:32:39,000
 So that's for some of us what we need to do.

542
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:48,000
 But for others of us, rest is found in Jesus.

543
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:51,000
 So for one, all of us need to come to Jesus.

