00:32:51,000 --> 00:32:57,000
 But I want to right now speak specifically to those of you who actually don't know Jesus fully yet.

545
00:32:57,000 --> 00:33:05,000
 And I want to give an opportunity to actually come to Jesus and to become a Christian.

546
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:08,000
 And it's easy to come to church.

547
00:33:08,000 --> 00:33:11,000
 Sometimes we think coming to church makes us a Christian.

548
00:33:11,000 --> 00:33:14,000
 Coming to church doesn't make you a Christian.

549
00:33:14,000 --> 00:33:19,000
 Sometimes we grow up in a Christian country, and we feel like I'm a Christian because I grew up in this country.

550
00:33:19,000 --> 00:33:23,000
 Growing up in a Christian country doesn't make you a Christian.

551
00:33:23,000 --> 00:33:29,000
 Growing up in a Christian family does not make you a Christian.

552
00:33:29,000 --> 00:33:34,000
 There comes this point in our lives where we have to make our own decision.

553
00:33:34,000 --> 00:33:37,000
 Am I going to receive Jesus into my heart?

554
00:33:37,000 --> 00:33:40,000
 Or am I going to cross that line?

