00:33:51,000 --> 00:33:59,000
 You know, we admit that we're sinners, that we're broken people, that we have this need for Jesus for His forgiveness.

558
00:33:59,000 --> 00:34:06,000
 Believe that Jesus is Savior and Redeemer and Lord, that He died, that He rose.

559
00:34:06,000 --> 00:34:11,000
 And then finally confess, confess that Jesus is your Lord.

560
00:34:11,000 --> 00:34:15,000
 Not somebody else's, not your neighbor's, but your Lord.

561
00:34:15,000 --> 00:34:19,000
 And so I'm going to lead you in a prayer.

562
00:34:19,000 --> 00:34:26,000
 You can quietly pray it along in your heart, and you can become a Christian and take that step.

