00:35:21,000 --> 00:35:39,000
 I believe that you died on the cross for my sins, and that you rose again so that I can have new life and be forgiven.

571
00:35:39,000 --> 00:35:48,000
 And so Jesus, I invite you in my heart right now.

572
00:35:48,000 --> 00:35:53,000
 I confess that you are my Lord and my Savior.

573
00:35:53,000 --> 00:35:56,000
 Will you come into my life?

574
00:35:56,000 --> 00:36:03,000
 Will you fill me with your Holy Spirit?

575
00:36:03,000 --> 00:36:08,000
 And I pray this in your name, Jesus.

