00:37:01,000 --> 00:37:08,000
 I just want to invite you to stretch out your hands just as a symbol of just wanting to receive from God.

584
00:37:08,000 --> 00:37:15,000
 I just want to pray over you.

585
00:37:15,000 --> 00:37:23,000
 Jesus, thank you so much that you are the one in whom we truly find rest.

586
00:37:23,000 --> 00:37:33,000
 Thank you that you love every single person here, that you know every single person, you know what's going on, you know the challenges that they're facing.

587
00:37:33,000 --> 00:37:45,000
 And I just pray right now that you will come, that you will meet them, that you release the peace of God over every single heart right now.

